           <h1 class=""> Structure</h1>
           <p><em>To allow for the Top Navbar, the first container chould also have the class of <strong>content</strong>, this will add a top margin so that it drops below the navbar.</em></p>
           <h2>Grid Structure</h2>
           <p><em>The Grid Structure has been amended slighly from the Bootstrap Default. We have adjusted the column-gutters to be <strong>20px</strong> instead of the original 30px.</em></p>
